%% Sequence Diagram: Status Sync on Workflow Completion (FR-006)

sequenceDiagram
    participant Orch as Orchestrator (Finalize)
    participant Git as Git
    participant State as state.json
    participant MCP as Atlassian MCP
    participant Jira as Jira Cloud
    participant BL as BACKLOG.md

    Note over Orch: STEP 4: FINALIZE

    Orch->>Orch: Human Review Checkpoint (if enabled)

    Orch->>Git: Merge feature branch to main
    Git-->>Orch: Merge successful

    Note over Orch: NEW: Jira Status Sync
    Orch->>State: Read active_workflow.jira_ticket_id
    State-->>Orch: "PROJ-1234"

    alt jira_ticket_id is null/missing
        Note over Orch: Local-only workflow, skip Jira sync
    else jira_ticket_id exists
        Orch->>MCP: updateStatus("PROJ-1234", "Done")
        alt Sync Successful
            MCP->>Jira: POST transition PROJ-1234 to Done
            Jira-->>MCP: 200 OK
            MCP-->>Orch: success
            Note over Orch: Log: "Jira ticket PROJ-1234 transitioned to Done"
        else Sync Failed
            MCP-->>Orch: error (permissions/workflow rules/network)
            Note over Orch: WARNING: Jira sync failed<br/>(non-blocking, continue finalize)
        end

        Orch->>BL: Mark item [x], move to Completed section
    end

    Note over Orch: Continue normal finalize
    Orch->>State: Collect phase snapshots
    Orch->>State: Prune state
    Orch->>State: Move to workflow_history<br/>(includes jira_ticket_id, jira_sync_status)
    Orch->>State: Clear active_workflow
